<br>
The secret to pulling Hards? Others have hinted at it here but the secret is to pull with harmony of sound and split the mobs on the way to the camp. SSoQ is a suckers play in LDoN hard. Don't even bother wasting your time with it.<br>
<br>
I leave a HUGE amount of room between my group and the mobs. Usually two open rooms at least, defnitely enough room to split mobs.<br>
<br>
