<br>
If you mez a mob closest to you, only the mobs in assist range of that mob will agro... not the ones within assist range of the assisting mobs. (I know that doesn't sound very clear... but oh well).<br>
<br>
And yes, you will probably get multiples every time... although if you did it right, you will have one (or sometimes two) mobs mezzed... although if you have a high mana / ft rate, you can fade off the mobs your mezzing and get singles every time.<br>
<br>
